

#### How I memorize:
-I Create an Image with data e.g: a triangle
-I Use Mnemonic > I_CRUD
-I use Action verbs
-I Create Mini-Mental Story

--------

It helps me (এটি আমাকে ______ সাহায্য করে) exchange/account/save/make/know/grasp/compare/conduct/plan/engage 

It allows me(এটি আমাকে____অনুমতি দেয়) to borrow and lend.
It lets me(এটি আমাকে___) borrow and lend.
**More formal: "Allows" generally has a slightly more formal tone than "lets."












